Package: lapr
Title: Fast Linear Assignment Solver
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R:
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Modern, tidy implementation of the Hungarian and Jonker-Volgenant 
    algorithms for solving linear assignment problems. Supports rectangular 
    matrices, NA/Inf masking for forbidden assignments, data frame inputs with
    tidy output, batch solving of multiple problems, and finding k-best optimal
    solutions via Murty's algorithm.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
